component_description: Detection results for Goal Reminder Prompt

elements.label: Goal Reminder Prompt > Title
elements.description: Bold dark gray text reading 'Get a daily reminder to meet your goal' centered at the top of the main content area
elements.explanation: Bounding box closely matches the text element, with only minimal extra vertical and horizontal padding.

component_description: Detection results for Page Header > Status Bar

elements.label: Page Header > Status Bar > Time
elements.description: Small text displaying '9:41' in the top-left corner of the screen status bar
elements.explanation: Bounding box is well-aligned around the time text with minimal extra space, showing high accuracy.

elements.label: Page Header > Status Bar > Connectivity Icons
elements.description: Signal strength and Wi-Fi indicators displayed in the top-right area of the status bar
elements.explanation: Box effectively covers the connectivity icons with slight extra padding but remains precise and correct.

elements.label: Page Header > Status Bar > Battery Icon
elements.description: Battery icon showing charge level positioned at the far top-right of the screen
elements.explanation: Box closely frames the battery icon but includes minor adjacent space; overall, fit is visually appropriate.

elements.label: Page Header > Navigation > Back Button
elements.description: Gray left-pointing arrow positioned in the top-left below the status bar
elements.explanation: The bounding box tightly fits the back arrow in the top-left corner with minimal excess area. High alignment with the described element.

elements.label: Page Header > Navigation > Progress Bar
elements.description: Yellow horizontal progress bar extending across most of the top portion below the status bar
elements.explanation: Box accurately contains the yellow horizontal progress bar with slight extra padding on the right but overall correct in size and position.

component_description: Detection results for Goal Reminder Prompt > Mascot

elements.label: Goal Reminder Prompt > Mascot > Character
elements.description: Green cartoon owl with large eyes positioned on the left side of the middle section
elements.explanation: Box tightly covers the green owl character with minor extra coverage toward the right to include the bell; fairly accurate for the mascot.

elements.label: Goal Reminder Prompt > Mascot > Bell Icon
elements.description: Small yellow bell icon held by the green owl character
elements.explanation: Box is too large, including owl's head and whitespace; corrected to fit only the yellow bell the owl is holding.

elements.label: Goal Reminder Prompt > Mascot > Speech Bubble
elements.description: White speech bubble containing text 'Just in case you forget!' extending from the green owl character
elements.explanation: Box captures nearly all of the speech bubble and text with only a minimal margin on the left side; highly accurate.

elements.label: Continue Button > Button
elements.description: Wide green rectangular button with white text 'CONTINUE' spanning the bottom portion of the screen
elements.explanation: Bounding box tightly surrounds the 'CONTINUE' button with only minimal padding on the sides. Very accurate.

component_description: Detection results for Notification Permission Dialog

elements.label: Notification Permission Dialog > Container
elements.description: White rounded rectangle container with light gray border occupying the middle portion of the screen
elements.explanation: The original box covers the entire visible image, while the dialog is only centered. Box updated to fit the actual dialog container.

elements.label: Notification Permission Dialog > App Icon
elements.description: Small green square icon with cartoon eyes, positioned within the upper portion of the notification dialog
elements.explanation: Box tightly frames the app icon with only slight extra margin at the top and bottom.

elements.label: Notification Permission Dialog > Message
elements.description: Black text explaining that 'duolingo.com' would like to send notifications, centered in the dialog box
elements.explanation: The box closely fits the central notification permission message, with minor horizontal padding.

elements.label: Notification Permission Dialog > Additional Info
elements.description: Small gray text about notifications settings in Safari, positioned in the lower portion of the dialog
elements.explanation: Box fits the small gray 'website preferences' text with minor overhang right and left.

elements.label: Notification Permission Dialog > Block Button
elements.description: Light gray rectangular button labeled 'BLOCK' positioned on the left side of the dialog's bottom section
elements.explanation: Box tightly frames the 'BLOCK' button, horizontally and vertically.

elements.label: Notification Permission Dialog > Allow Button
elements.description: Blue rectangular button labeled 'ALLOW' positioned on the right side of the dialog's bottom section
elements.explanation: Box snugly captures 'ALLOW' button with almost no unnecessary padding.

elements.label: Notification Permission Dialog > Indicator Arrow
elements.description: Blue upward-pointing arrow below the notification permission dialog
elements.explanation: Box fits the blue arrow below the dialog accurately, containing the full icon.
